pageContext.description: This appears to have been intended for the chase and not for warfare, as similar one are generally found in old hunting grounds. 2 holes which are practically filled with encrusted metal.
pageContext.surface: Smooth. Bronze coloured shades from golden to reddish and dark brown. Very tiny pits all over.
